{"type":"answer","id":183028,"parentType":"question","parentId":4737,"uid":25065,"contents":"<center><i>浪淘沙 南唐後主</i></center><br>\n<center><i>簾外雨潺潺，春意闌珊。&nbsp;</i></center><br>\n<center><i>羅衾不耐五更寒。&nbsp;</i></center><br>\n<center><i><u>夢裡不知身是客，一餉貪歡。</u>&nbsp;</i></center><br>\n<center><i>獨自莫憑闌，無限江山。</i></center><br>\n<center><i>別時容易見時難。&nbsp;</i></center><br>\n<center><i>流水落花春去也，天上人間。&nbsp;</i></center><br>\n<br>\n詩詞是文學，也是哲學、人生學。望遠山重山，碧水縈還。<br>\n<br>\n敬白","date":"2020-02-28","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}